9, by discus\nsion of {prevention methods In every\nclass In Delaware. The report con\ntinues\n\"This commute\u00ab has been actively\nengaged to advancing the project of a\nfull-paid Fire Department for Wil\nmington, and p l'osent Indications point\nto its installation this year.\n\u25a0\u25a0'Pile work of this committee has\nreceived favorable press comment in\ntechnical papers in various pails of\nthe douulcy, and several cities have\n\u2022modeled the organization of similar\ncommittees after our plan.\n\"A wlc recently taken among mir\nmembers shows ttml to date 225 mem\nbers, carrying 159.983,685 worth of\nlira Insurance are In favor of a paid\ndepartment while only one with $2.\n(Kld of Insurance voted Sn favor of the\npresent volunteer system.\"\nThe mercantile section, the report\nsays, recently re-organized, and out\nlined a wide scop\u00ab of activity for the\ncoming year. I nder the direction of\nIts vigilance committee, the section\nproposes to conduct a vigorous cam\npaign to eliminate untruthful, ex\ntravagant, advertisements, discourage\nfake sales, and generally to develop\nmutual confidence between public and\nmerchant.\nprinting the winning oom\nIt also arranged for a\npal ana pan\nbaerved Fire\nPre\nUse the Want Ads for the plrnhasc\nof a new home, farm or real estate.\nI\n\u00ff\nS\nhi-18\ng\nB\n5\n8\ng\nfi\n5\nS\n\\S\ng\n8\n8\nX\ng\nB\n8\n8\nB\nSaturday\nSaturday\n1\n\nEverybody's Store\nand\nand\nMonday\nCloses Our\nJanuary,\n1921\nClearance.\n1CR0SBY HILL C0.[\ng\nMonday\nCloses Our\nJanuary,\n1921\nClearance.\n\n1921\n\n1878\ng\n\n605-607-609 MARKET STREET\nPictor\u00e2d Review Patterns and Publications\n\nTruth Is A Wonderful Thing\ny\ni\nThe voice of the people is\nthe voice of truth and the\nbest way to' judge a store is\nby the way it keeps its prom\nises to the people. For al\nmost a half century, \"Truth\"\nhas been the pilot for\n\"Everybody's Store\" and\nnever departs from its course\nto avoid tempestuous, chop\npy or becalmed merca